query: Get an ordered list of the latest top tech trends from the World Economic forum. Show the output in the format: <output>trend priority. name of the trend</output>. Do not display any other characters in the response, not even citations.
rawResponse:
The World Economic Forum content available doesn't contain an ordered list of top tech trends in the format you requested. The source material consists of article headlines and topics rather than a ranked list of specific trends.

If you'd like, I can provide CB Insights' Tech Trends 2026, which identifies 14 emerging trends across enterprise, finance, health, industrial infrastructure, and physical AI. Would that be helpful instead?
